product.title: Kobe Bryant Lakers Jersey
product.description: Commemorate one of the most recognizable players in NBA history at our Kobe Bryant Shop. The Black Mamba was a five-time champion who played for the LA Lakers for the duration of his career, and he's just been named in the 2020 NBA Hall of Fame Class. At the official online store of the NBA, we offer the latest Kobe Bryant jerseys, including the new Kobe reversible jersey from Mitchell and Ness, complete with his #8 on one side and #24 on the other. In addition to jerseys, we've got tons of Kobe apparel, shoes, and merchandise. Our large selection of Kobe Bryant "Black Mamba" t-shirts,
